🍔 Food Delivery Analytics Dashboard | Power BI
📌 Project Overview

This project is a complete Food Delivery Analytics Dashboard built using Power BI. The dashboard provides end-to-end analysis of restaurant performance, customer behavior, order trends, revenue generation, and delivery efficiency.

The goal of this project is to transform raw transactional data into meaningful business insights that can help management make data-driven decisions.


















# 🍔 Food Delivery Analytics Dashboard | Power BI

## 📌 Project Overview

This project is a complete Food Delivery Analytics Dashboard built using Power BI. The dashboard provides end-to-end analysis of restaurant performance, customer behavior, order trends, revenue generation, and delivery efficiency.

The goal of this project is to transform raw transactional data into meaningful business insights that can help management make data-driven decisions.

---

## 🎯 Business Problem

Food delivery businesses generate thousands of orders every day. Without proper analytics, it becomes difficult to:

* Monitor revenue performance
* Identify top-performing restaurants
* Understand customer behavior
* Track delivery efficiency
* Reduce cancellations and delays
* Improve operational performance

This dashboard solves these challenges by providing interactive visualizations and KPI tracking.

---

## 📊 Dataset Information

The dataset contains four tables:

### 1. Orders (Fact Table)

* Order ID
* Restaurant ID
* Customer ID
* Order Date
* Order Value
* Quantity
* Delivery Time
* Order Status

### 2. Customers

* Customer ID
* Customer Name
* Customer Type
* City
* Signup Date

### 3. Restaurants

* Restaurant ID
* Restaurant Name
* Cuisine
* Rating
* Location
* Cost for Two
* Restaurant Type

### 4. Date Table

* Date
* Year
* Quarter
* Month
* Day

---

## ⭐ Key KPIs

The dashboard tracks:

* Total Revenue
* Total Orders
* Total Customers
* Average Order Value (AOV)
* Average Delivery Time
* Delivered Orders
* Cancelled Orders
* Delayed Orders
* Delivery Success Rate

---

## 📈 Dashboard Pages

### 1️⃣ Executive Overview

Provides a high-level business summary.

Visuals:

* KPI Cards
* Revenue Trend
* Orders Trend
* Revenue by Customer Type
* Revenue by Order Status

---

### 2️⃣ Sales & Revenue Analytics

Analyzes revenue performance.

Visuals:

* Revenue by Cuisine
* Revenue by Restaurant Type
* Revenue by Location
* Monthly Revenue Trend
* Top Restaurants by Revenue

---

### 3️⃣ Customer Analytics

Analyzes customer behavior and segmentation.

Visuals:

* Customer Type Distribution
* Customer Signup Trend
* Revenue by Customer Type
* Top Customers
* Orders per Customer

---

### 4️⃣ Restaurant & Delivery Analytics

Evaluates restaurant and delivery performance.

Visuals:

* Top Restaurants
* Rating vs Revenue Analysis
* Cuisine Performance
* Delivery Status Analysis
* Delivery Time by Location

---

## 🏗 Data Model

Star Schema Design:

Orders (Fact Table)

├── Customers

├── Restaurants

└── Date Table

Relationships:

* Orders → Customers
* Orders → Restaurants
* Orders → Date Table

---


